All Classes

Class Description
Cache
Own class for cache objects so instances of filled custom database objects can be cached.
Column
Custom annotation to classify class fields as database columns.
Config
Singleton class for database connection data config loading.
CreateTableQuery
SQL query class for create table operations.
DatabaseConnection
Singleton implementation of the database connection.
Entity
Every database table is being represented as a Entity class object within the framework.
Field
Every database column gets represented as a field.
ForeignKey
Custom annotation to classify class fields as foreign key relations in database.
InsertQuery
Sql query class for insert queries.
Manager
Manager class operates as a single Instance for legal checks and other operational tests
MetaData
Class for all kinds of metadata extraction, handling, manipulation, etc...
Query
generic interface for sql queries.
QueryLanguage
Helper interface for various sql query language.
SelectQuery
SQL query class for select statements.
Table
Custom annotation to classify a class as a database table.
